Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要的東西馬上丟掉 這是我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以養成了整理物品的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能留在身邊的東西終究有限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總要輕裝上陣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件雨衣… 是和友香一起去買的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 你正在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs70\pos(922,114)\bord4\shad2\4c&HFFFFDD&\3c&HCABD76&\c&HF7F4F3&}雨衣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(876,184)\bord4\shad2\4c&HFFFFDD&\3c&HCABD76&\c&HF7F4F3&}～友香 你正在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身材好 人也聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是個怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還爬山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人不怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是 國中時我給人的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 又受傷了？ 在山裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 稍微擦破皮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子一個人去爬山不危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 友香 替我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是一個人爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都自由自在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你又要去爬高山了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝備夠嗎？ 真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次帶名產回來給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別著急啦 不會給你添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有那麼危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒給友香添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 心裡似乎還有一種異樣的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 心裡好不舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楓！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又受這麼重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微扭了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪是稍微扭了一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼沒事啊 這還算沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是被討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不至於那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又沒給她添麻煩…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算我這麼想 友香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算裝出笑臉向她道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒認真聽過她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是橫衝直撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顧周圍往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香擔心我 我也覺得不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 友香並不是表面應和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是真心的在擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我卻沒認真對待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個人真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人一起走的時候 要考慮對方的步調
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人交往也是一個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走得太快 拉開太遠 就該停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待對方追上自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那麼替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會注意安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說這些 是不是晚了點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也說得太超過了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一時忍不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楓？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所缺少的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是整理不好的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕誰都不肯搭理自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香聽我說 我以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有人擔心 有人生氣 是多麼幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想買件新雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在穿的已經破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跟你一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 稍微有些興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 機會難得 想讓你再穿出點女人味來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是不是太女性化了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣正好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楓你身材又好 個子又高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 多可惜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下來去買雨衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢 種類好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山的時候雨衣很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼誇張？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只防雨 還能防風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 更多時候用來防寒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在山上 雨水會從四面八方襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨傘不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說好貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了登山附加各種功能就貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好輕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 又輕又結實又防水 還能透汗呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整合了這麼多功能的料子 自然就貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還有防水手套 防雨裙之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這種衝鋒褲 穿著鞋都能穿進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前啊 登山的時候下雨了很要命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我好像明白你其實也在照顧自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 打算買哪件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件看著不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顏色和你很搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就它了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 還是這件的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我逛這麼久 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太見外了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都說了 對你在做的事情感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 的確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你啊 三不五時少一根筋 讓人不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 遇到危險就打電話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你來救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣的表情不可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楓！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件衝鋒衣 尺寸不合適 已經穿不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎麼捨得丟掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說友香 現在在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 友香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那陪我去買東西好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去所澤 看看登山裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少請你吃蛋糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那30分後 在車站前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐好 我想去爬谷川岳 想請教學姐一下（>人<）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發送！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前友香擔心我 這次大概輪到我去擔心小葵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經孤獨地走著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在已經不再孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身邊有友香和小葵她們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 友香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楓好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼又穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不穿出女人味來 多可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從前就跟你說很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 UFO！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你！別矇混過關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣的表情不可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楓！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不站住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待續
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,並んで歩いてたら自然に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,二人三脚なってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:23.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,透明リボンで結ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりで描く夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:32.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ふたりなら立体的になる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,キュンときて上昇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,スタッカートみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:43.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,胸を叩くワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:47.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それに つきあってくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,気の合う Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球色パレット
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,混ぜて明日は何色?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,不思議 不安より
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:09.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しみの容量が増えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,また明日！ヤッホー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}肩並肩走著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}自然就會挽起雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:23.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}透明的蝴蝶結 繫緊兩人的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一個人的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:32.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}兩人一起就會變得立體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}跟著心跳上升！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:43.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}昂揚感像斷奏音符般拍打胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:51.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}身邊還有陪伴我的知心 Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}地球湛藍調色板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}調出明天未知的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真奇妙 不但沒有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:09.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快樂的容量反而更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}明天再見！YAHOO
